32dbc85cb1cd754d5960462e","tid":1357152,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中聯辦亂港</span></span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721西環正式宣言 上環36槍 槍槍打頭 </span></span><br />\n和平示威者被警方惡意攻擊 連開36槍 槍槍打頭 <br />\n更於橋上向下向頭部發射 和平示威者身受重傷 <br />\n警方更用強光阻礙記者拍攝現場情況 <br />\n<br />\n警察之權力已凌駕市民生命財產之上 <br />\n港府警方上至 高官 局長 下至 政府公務員 低級警員 <br />\n協助 中共中聯辦 於 612 - 721 期間 <br />\n不斷以非法及不人道之暴力行為 <br />\n意圖消滅所有持反對聲音的平民 <br />\n卻不作反對 <br />\n反之竟合作出賣港人前途 打壓無辜示威者<br />\n<br />\n【文宣包】<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1356661/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1356661/page/1</a><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">港府已被廢 香港前途未卜</span></span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">中共下令香港警察與黑社會合作合法亂港殺人</span></span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人生命安全被中國共產黨及<br />\n香港政府視為政治籌碼<br />\n利用恐怖勢力傷害所有平民<br />\n </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">---------------------------------------</span></span><br />\n中國及港政府所有不人道之行動 <br />\n已令香港不再安全 <br />\n並再難以保持經濟地位及自由民主法治社會<br />\n所有香港人都需參與社會運動 <br />\n保護自己的生命安全 人權自由 民主法治 經濟地位<br />\n以上等等被政府損害的權利<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n---------------------------------------</span></span><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"7924853b636f865dbc5ff4fcbb458e1acd43bd86","tid":1357152,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af7a38980918677342ba32119ed32efd7fb7942","tid":1357152,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3992fa563f8e2c7e2ffdbce9775a82068ed66f62","tid":1357152,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe995ce5ff32b858a04da53443b9b3342eb86ea","tid":1357152,"uid":85498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"律政司唔會告"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"下任呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估個政府為左拎民意會郁邊個啊啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:48:14.000Z","msg":"我地奪權之後告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}